 133: _DE_MONOLOG_DIRECTIVE: Final = """\
 134: 
 135: Answer in **German**, even if the stimulus is in English. Write a single \
 136: self-addressed monolog of 80窶・60 German words (竕・100窶・00 \
 137: tokens). Do not address an interlocutor; do not name the questioner. \
 138: Use the Critique-of-Pure-Reason register: transcendental, a priori, an \
 139: sich, kategorischer Imperativ, where the topic permits. Return ONLY the \
 140: monolog text 窶・no preamble, no quotation marks, no JSON, no \
 141: chain-of-thought."""
