   1: """Unit tests for ``scripts/m9-c-adopt/de_focused_monolog_collector.py``.
   2: 
   3: The collector is a Plan B (Candidate C hybrid retrain) driver. SGLang HTTP
   4: is not exercised here 窶・the tests exercise the post-hoc filter chain
   5: (language, length, marker density, trigram loop detector) and the stimulus
   6: subset selection logic that determines which kant.yaml stimuli feed the
   7: de-monolog corpus.
   8: 
   9: The script lives at ``scripts/m9-c-adopt/de_focused_monolog_collector.py``
  10: which is not on the default Python path (``-`` in dirname), so it is
  11: loaded via ``importlib.util.spec_from_file_location`` exactly like
  12: ``tests/test_m9_c_adopt_pilot.py``.
  13: """
